  OpenTelemetry abstraction in src/tracing so sessions and events emitted by rrweb are properly associated with the correct spans. 3) Integrating our core implementation such that it
  becomes another component such as Telemetry in the SDK that becomes initialized when the SDK starts (provided the component is enabled) and de-initialized when execution is over, if
  applicable. 4) Transport, we need to create a strategy to send this data to the Rollbar API just like we send occurrences, except that this data can ONLY be sent together with an
  occurrence. This would imply some internal management because, and this is very important, we only want to send the last 5 minutes of a recording. This may get tricky since rrweb first
  even is a full snapshot of the DOM structure, which is something we absolutely want to preserve. BUT, we can take this progressively and tackle complexity as we go. And finally, 5)
