  1. First create a standalone implementation to ensure rrweb works correctly with our architecture
  2. Add tests for the standalone implementation
  3. Integrate with Tracing to associate recordings with sessions and spans
  4. Add configuration options to control recording behavior
  5. Expose API methods for manual control
  6. Add documentation and examples to show how to use the new functionality

  Testing Strategy

  1. Unit tests for the RrwebRecorder class
    - Test event recording and time-based filtering
    - Test pruning of old events
